-- Torunlar of Turkey halts construction at all projects in wake of deadly accident
-- By Ayla Jean Yackley
-- Mon Sep 08, 2014 05:36AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Sept 8 (Reuters) - Turkish real-estate developer Torunlar REIT <TRGYO.IS> said on Monday it has halted construction activities at all of its projects for five days following an accident that killed 10 workers at an Istanbul residential project.

